but for substance I haue not omitted any thing that
may much import, considering what the occasion, and
subiect of the Conference was; to wit, that Paper
written by M. Fisher, in which he proued the Roman
Church, and those who agree in Fayth with it, to be
that Company, of whome euery one must learne what
